   <head>To the deuout READER.</head>
   <p>
      <seg rend="decorInit">I</seg> Had not pur<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>posed to en<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>large the <hi>last Edition,</hi> saue that the <hi>importunitie</hi> of many <hi>deuoutly</hi> disposed, preuailed with mee, to <hi>adde</hi> some points, and to <hi>amplifie</hi> others. To satisfie whose godly requests, I haue done my best <hi>inde<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>uour</hi>: and with all <hi>finished</hi>
      <pb facs="14"/>
all that I entend in this <hi>argument.</hi> If thou shalt hereby reape any more <hi>profit,</hi> giue God the more <hi>praise</hi>: and remember him in thy <hi>Prayers,</hi> who hath vowed both his <hi>life</hi> and his <hi>labours</hi> to further <hi>thy saluation</hi> as his <hi>owne.</hi> Farewell in the <hi>Lord Iesus.</hi>
   </p>
</div>
